			<sumFormula>LiAlSi 2 O 6</sumFormula>
			<common:generalComment xml:lang="en">Spodumene is a pyroxene mineral typically found in lithium-rich pegmatites. It is usually associated with other lithium minerals such as lepidolite, eucryptite, and petalite. It has a chemical composition of LiAlSi 2 O 6 but small amounts of sodium sometimes substitute for lithium. It is an important ore of lithium and a source of ceramic materials. It can also be pink, lilac, or green. Crystals are prismatic, flattened, and typically striated along their length. Gem varieties of the mineral usually exhibit strong pleochroism.</common:generalComment>
			<common:generalComment xml:lang="zh">橄榄石是一种辉石矿物，通常存在于富含锂的伟晶岩中。它通常与其他锂矿物（如鳞片石、桉石和花瓣石）伴生。它的化学成分为 LiAlSi 2 O 6，但有时会以少量钠代替锂。它是一种重要的锂矿石，也是陶瓷材料的来源。它也可以呈粉红色、淡紫色或绿色。晶体呈棱柱状，扁平，通常沿其长度方向呈条纹状。宝石级矿物通常具有强烈的多色性。</common:generalComment>
